 TI\u1ebeP SLNA VS C\u1ea6N TH\u01a0</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3787","checkdouble":"189350"},{"date":"15:38 23/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 19h00 ng\u00e0y 23/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/ha-noi-vs-da-nang-vong-15-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 23/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 23/6.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-da-nang-vong-15-vleague-2018-372-189355.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I VS \u0110\u00c0 N\u1eb4NG</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3786","checkdouble":"189355"},{"date":"17:28 23/06","title":"Thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, HLV T\u00e0i Em t\u1ed1 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/thua-nguoc-tai-pho-nui-hlv-tai-em-to-hagl-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2>HLV T\u00e0i Em t\u1ed1 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trong tai tran HAGL\" title=\"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i tr\u1eadn HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/thua-nguoc-tai-pho-nui-hlv-tai-em-to-hagl-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 thi\u00ean v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y trong khi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 Da Sylva.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb n\u00ean m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u1ecb HLV sinh n\u0103m 1982 n\u00f3i: &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t penalty l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi sau \u0111\u00f3, Da Sylva b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m th\u00ec tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u1ea1i cho l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf. Sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00f4i y\u00eau c\u1ea7u BTC c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i xem l\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i s\u1edbm th\u1ed5i c\u00f2i k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC b\u1ecb thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i b\u1edfi trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i canh th\u1eddi gian, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft 4 ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed5i c\u00f2i. Ngo\u00e0i ra, trong th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL, th\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng ra tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&rdquo;, T\u00e0i Em cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 12 v\u00e0o tay TP.HCM &nbsp;ho\u1eb7c Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua-168-189318.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua-168-189318.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 vua</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00ec l\u1ee3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua HAGL nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3785","checkdouble":"189359"},{"date":"17:42 23/06","title":"HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 trong th\u1eddi gian qua","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/9/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-phong-do-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-trong-thoi-gian-qua.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian qua.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 22/6, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy nhi\u00ean C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 ghi li\u1ec1n 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u201cG\u1ed7\u201d ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HAGL th\u1eddi gian qu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HAGL th\u1eddi gian qu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng World Cup c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Minh \u0111\u00e3 cho r\u1eb1ng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c trong d\u1ecbp World Cup 2018 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HAGL sa s\u00fat th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u1edf V-League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"V-League di\u1ec5n ra trong d\u1ecbp World Cup th\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean. World Cup c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9c xem n\u00ean th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng\", HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC t\u1ed1i qua 22/6.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng HAGL t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft: \"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Sau ba tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, c\u00e1c em ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean \u1ea5y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, HAGL s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec3 thua tan t\u00e1c 0-3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201c\"H\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i to\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m, thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 n\u1eefa\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHAGL s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i 26/6 t\u1edbi. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi t\u1ed1p 3 tr\u00ean BXH.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua-168-189318.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua-168-189318.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 vua</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00ec l\u1ee3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua HAGL nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-tran-thang-nhoc-cua-hagl-truoc-sai-gon-fc-421-189290.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/thay-gi-sau-tran-thang-nhoc-cua-hagl-truoc-sai-gon-fc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-tran-thang-nhoc-cua-hagl-truoc-sai-gon-fc-421-189290.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC?</span><br>\r\nTrong l\u1ea7n t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Pleiku chi\u1ec1u 22/6, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sau tr\u1eadn thua \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nguoc-tai-pho-nui-hlv-tai-em-to-hagl-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi-168-189359.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/thua-nguoc-tai-pho-nui-hlv-tai-em-to-hagl-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nguoc-tai-pho-nui-hlv-tai-em-to-hagl-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi-168-189359.html\">Thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, HLV T\u00e0i Em t\u1ed1 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3784","checkdouble":"189360"},{"date":"13:24 23/06","title":"Sao Man City c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/14/sao-man-city-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Barca mua Ilkay Gundogan th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man City thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca nh\u1eafm Gundogan n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap danh hi\u1ec7u, Barca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. HLV Ernesto Valverde \u01b0u ti\u00ean n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Barca mua Ilkay Gundogan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pep Guardiola ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Barca mua Ilkay Gundogan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/1/Pep-Guardiola-ngan-can-Barca-mua-Ilkay-Gundogan-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Ilkay Gundogan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAndres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay s\u00e2n Camp Nou, vi\u1ec7c Valverde mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. T\u1edd Mirror c\u1ee7a Anh v\u00e0 Don Balon c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou quan t\u00e2m Gundogan c\u1ee7a Man City.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Gundogan l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Man City, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n t\u1edbi 48 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. \u1ede Premier League anh ra s\u00e2n 30/38 tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh v\u1eeba c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ghi 6 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady Pep Guardiola ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 anh ta ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Man City nh\u1ea3 Gundogan, Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Man xanh ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecf ra 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 t\u1eeb Dortmund.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gundogan t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-chi-35-trieu-bang-mua-sao-man-city-180-188578.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca mua Ilkay Gundogan </span>th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man City thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gundogan\" title=\"Gundogan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/27/Inter-Milan-muon-mua-Ilkay-Gundogan-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gundogan t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin Barca quan t\u00e2m Gundogan, HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i. The Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Gundogan v\u1edbi Man City c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020, anh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad. \u1ede b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi Man xanh s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPep mu\u1ed1n Gundogan s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Fernandinho, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u HLV Barca t\u1eeb b\u1ecf ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3783","checkdouble":"189345"},{"date":"14:38 23/06","title":"L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/7/lo-ben-do-moi-cua-mateo-kovacic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Spurs ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kovacic quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 14 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf hai m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/Tottenham-muon-mua-Mateo-Kovacic-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 24, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u00f4i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Marca, HLV Lopetegui s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Kovacic m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/kovacic-muon-roi-real-180-189338.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kovacic r\u1eddi Real Madrid</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Spurs ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/lo-ben-do-moi-cua-mateo-kovacic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Pochettino s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Dembele \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU, AC Milan v\u00e0 PSG theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Dembele s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Mateo Kovacic t\u1eeb Real Madrid. HLV Pochettino \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Spurs l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKovacic gia nh\u1eadp Real t\u1eeb Inter v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e8 2015. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Los Blancos nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Spurs \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3782","checkdouble":"189349"},{"date":"13:44 23/06","title":"Man City mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU v\u1ee5 trung v\u1ec7 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/4/8/barca-dung-luong-khung-du-do-sieu-trung-ve-cua-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a M.U. \u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Man xanh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Boateng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n7 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Bayern Munich trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/Man-City-muon-mua-Jerome-Boateng-voi-gia-50-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Jerome Boateng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Boateng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge c\u1ee7a Bayern \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Bayern Munich s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Boateng s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30 v\u00e0 c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d kh\u00f4ng m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City chi 50 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Boateng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng, Pep \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Etihad. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Boateng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn ch\u01a1i cho Man xanh nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Boateng Ronaldo\" title=\"Boateng Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/5/26/mu-nham-sao-khung-tuyen-duc-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City mu\u1ed1n chi 50 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Boateng\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Etihad \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Boateng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-khung-tuyen-duc-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189082.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Boateng</span>, \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Man xanh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Bayern Munich mong mu\u1ed1n t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Boateng ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n 31 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bayern Munich, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 19 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Bundesliga. Nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChi 50 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30 v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Boateng c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf s\u00e2n Etihad l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. N\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u1ea7n suy ngh\u0129 th\u1eadt k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3781","checkdouble":"189346"},{"date":"14:03 23/06","title":"HLV Emery mu\u1ed1n Arsenal mua sao Sevilla n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/hlv-emery-muon-arsenal-mua-sao-sevilla-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Ever Banega c\u1ee7a Sevilla, HLV Unai Emery r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal nh\u1eafm Banega n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJack Wilshere x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chia tay Arsenal theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Emirates \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Ever Banega c\u1ee7a Sevilla v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Ever Banega c\u1ee7a Sevilla v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Arsenal-muon-mua-Ever-Banega-cua-Sevilla-voi-gia-25-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Banega</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere bu\u1ed9c Arsenal ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Lucas Torreira c\u1ee7a Sampdoria, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sampdoria x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chu-tich-sampdoria-xac-nhan-ban-sao-khung-cho-arsenal-172-189024.html\" target=\"_blank\">Torreira s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Arsenal</span>. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i song HLV Emery v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Daily Star, Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Ever Banega c\u1ee7a Sevilla, HLV Unai Emery r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Ever Banega l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Sevilla, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n 50 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf La Liga anh c\u00f3 31 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal chi 25 trieu bang mua Banega\" title=\"Arsenal chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Banega\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/hlv-emery-muon-arsenal-mua-sao-sevilla-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Banega</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ghi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 Ever Banega khi\u1ebfn HLV Emery r\u1ea5t h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n Arsenal chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Ever Banega c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Emirates.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c Leno, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3780","checkdouble":"189347"},{"date":"14:24 23/06","title":"Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal, Mesut Ozil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/23/wilshere-roi-arsenal-mesut-ozil-da-cho-ngay-nay-tu-rat-lau-roi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jack Wilshere tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Wilshere v\u1edbi Arsenal c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2018, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n song hai b\u00ean v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Mesut-Ozil-muon-ao-so-10-cua-Jack-Wilshere-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wilshere tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi HLV Emery \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u00d4ng n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, song anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ra s\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Jack Wilshere ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ra \u0111i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/wilshere-chinh-thuc-roi-arsenal-172-188988.html\" target=\"_blank\">Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal </span>theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thu v\u1ec1 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 xu n\u00e0o t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, anh mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Southampton, West Ham v\u00e0 Everton \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Arsenal nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Wilshere \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m trung \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh Emery \u0111\u00e3 sai khi kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ozil vui nh\u1ea5t khi Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb khi Mesut Ozil c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o m\u00e0 Jack Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 \u0111eo t\u1eeb khi Robin van Persie chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi MU v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil muon khoac ao so 10\" title=\"Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/wilshere-roi-arsenal-mesut-ozil-da-cho-ngay-nay-tu-rat-lau-roi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 do\u00a0Wilshere b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 khi\u1ebfn Ozil ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 11. C\u1ee9 m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Ozil l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u01b0\u1edbc mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 song \u00f4ng Wenger t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng Jack Wilshere, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi Wilshere ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00ec s\u1ed1 10 \u1edf Arsenal v\u1eabn b\u1ecf tr\u1ed1ng, \u00f4ng Wenger t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh d\u00f9 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Ozil kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Arsenal th\u00ec Ozil \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u00e0y t\u1ecf \u01b0\u1edbc mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10. Theo Daily Mail, Ozil \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafn v\u1edbi HLV Emery r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mong mu\u1ed1n b\u1ea5y l\u00e2u c\u1ee7a Ozil s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Ozil \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o m\u00e0 anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh \u1edf \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3779","checkdouble":"189348"},{"date":"11:08 23/06","title":"Fan cu\u1ed3ng gi\u1ea3m\u2026 90 kg trong 6 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ronaldo","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/fan-cuong-giam-90-kg-trong-6-thang-de-duoc-gap-than-tuong-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"3778","checkdouble":"189340"},{"date":"11:15 23/06","title":"Ng\u00f4i sao Salah tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n danh d\u1ef1 \u1edf Chechnya","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/23/ngoi-sao-salah-tro-thanh-cong-dan-danh-du-o-chechnya.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Ramzan Kadyrov c\u1ee7a Chechnya \u0111\u00e3 trao quy\u1ec1n c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n danh d\u1ef1 cho Mohamed Salah trong m\u1ed9t b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 chia tay \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u1ede World Cup 2018, \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Grozny, th\u1ee7 ph\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Chechnya l\u00e0m n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n. C\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u1edfi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Kadyrov c\u1ee7a Chechnya, v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Salah. \u00d4ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Liverpool.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/salah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKadyrov \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi xem phi\u00ean t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i Grozny v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 10/6. Sau khi xem kho\u1ea3ng 10 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y ng\u00f4i sao Salah \u0111\u00e2u, Kadyrov \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e1i xe \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n n\u01a1i Salah \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i (Salah ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng vai kh\u00f4ng tham gia bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp). T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Kadyrov \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Salah theo \u0111\u1ebfn SV\u0110, n\u01a1i c\u1ea3 hai ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 ch\u00e0o h\u1ecfi 5.000 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i Ai C\u1eadp t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 15/6, Kadyrov \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi t\u1eb7ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc b\u00e1nh l\u1edbn t\u1edbi tr\u1ea1i hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eebng sinh nh\u1eadt Salah. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, khi \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chia tay Grozny, Kadyrov \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i dinh th\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng v\u00e0 trao cho Salah quy\u1ec1n c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n danh d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Chechnya. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Grozny v\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay (gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng) \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Volgograd \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i Word Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Saudi Arabia. C\u1ea3 Ai C\u1eadp l\u1eabn Saudi Arabia \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3777","checkdouble":"189341"},{"date":"09:43 23/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 19h00 ng\u00e0y 23/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/23/nhan-dinh-ha-noi-vs-da-nang-19h00-ngay-236-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 23/6 (V\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 19h00 ng\u00e0y 236 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 19h00 ng\u00e0y 236 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/ha-noi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: 2-0</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a 2-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u0103m nay b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nghi k\u1ef5 cho r\u1eb1ng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 b\u1edfi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao nh\u1ea5t. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vui v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin th\u1ea5t thi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf v\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi quay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n SHB.\u0110N.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SHB.\u0110N. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, trong m\u00e0n t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u nay, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin n\u01a1i NHM v\u00e0 x\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i V\u0103n H\u1eadu &ndash; \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, SHB.\u0110N c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 h\u01a1n khi m\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Merlo, Anh Tu\u1ea5n, Phan V\u0103n Long&hellip; v\u00ec l\u00fd do t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng.&nbsp; <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nH\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC: V\u0103n C\u00f4ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ed3ng, V\u0103n Ki\u00ean, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Moses, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Th\u00e0nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Quang H\u1ea3i, Oseni.<br>\r\nSHB.\u0110N: Thanh B\u00ecnh, Christian, Anh Quang, V\u0103n Long, Nh\u1eadt T\u00e2n, Ti\u1ebfn D\u1ee5ng, Minh T\u00e2m, Thanh H\u1ea3i, Ng\u1ecdc&nbsp; Th\u1eafng, Kouassi, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3776","checkdouble":"189332"},{"date":"11:00 23/06","title":"Sao s\u00e1ng Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/2/kovacic-muon-roi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic v\u1eeba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn mong mu\u1ed1n chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t.</h2><h2>Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kovacic \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid t\u1eeb Inter v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00e8 2015. Nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Zidane.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Kovacic ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 14 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/kovacic-muon-roi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Kovacic kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Bernabeu. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u00ean t\u1edd Marca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 r\u1eddi Real Madrid. T\u00f4i y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c. N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho MU v\u00e0 Tottenham</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/dai-gia-moi-noi-tottenham-mo-so-huu-sao-xet-cua-real-172-130926.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Kovacic</span> nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb Real Madrid t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, v\u1edbi di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Spurs kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Real th\u00eam n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1edfi trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Kovacic v\u1edbi Real c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e2m. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1edbi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Fred nh\u01b0ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n kh\u00e1c sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Fellaini v\u00e0 Carrick. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Jose Mourinho s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Do \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/toa-sang-o-world-cup-lukaku-lot-tam-ngam-real-madrid-180-189261.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup, Lukaku l\u1ecdt t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-189259.html\">Real Madrid nh\u1eafm ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3775","checkdouble":"189338"}]}